---
title: Deployment Architecture
description: Complete infrastructure and deployment architecture for Hospeda platform
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% Users
    User[👤 User Browser]

    %% Edge & CDN Layer
    Edge[🌐 Vercel Edge Network]
    CDN[📦 CDN - Static Assets]

    %% Frontend Applications
    WebApp[🏠 Web App<br/>Astro SSR/Static<br/>Port: 4321]
    AdminApp[⚙️ Admin App<br/>TanStack Start SSR<br/>Port: 4322]

    %% API Layer
    APIApp[🔌 API<br/>Hono on Node.js<br/>Vercel Serverless<br/>Port: 3000]

    %% Database Layer
    NeonDB[(🗄️ Neon PostgreSQL<br/>Serverless<br/>Connection Pool)]

    %% External Services
    Clerk[🔐 Clerk<br/>Authentication]
    MercadoPago[💳 Mercado Pago<br/>Payments]
    Cloudinary[🖼️ Cloudinary<br/>Image Storage]

    %% Monitoring
    Analytics[📊 Vercel Analytics]
    Logs[📝 Vercel Logs]

    %% Environments
    subgraph Production
        ProdEdge[Production Edge]
        ProdAPI[Production API]
        ProdDB[(Production DB)]
    end

    subgraph Preview
        PreviewEdge[Preview Edge]
        PreviewAPI[Preview API]
        PreviewDB[(Preview DB)]
    end

    subgraph Development
        DevLocal[Local Server]
        DevDB[(Local PostgreSQL)]
    end

    %% Flow
    User -->|HTTPS| Edge
    Edge -->|Route| WebApp
    Edge -->|Route| AdminApp
    Edge -->|Static Assets| CDN

    WebApp -->|API Calls| APIApp
    AdminApp -->|API Calls| APIApp

    APIApp -->|SQL Queries| NeonDB
    APIApp -->|Verify JWT| Clerk
    APIApp -->|Process Payment| MercadoPago
    APIApp -->|Upload Images| Cloudinary

    APIApp -.->|Metrics| Analytics
    APIApp -.->|Error Logs| Logs
    WebApp -.->|Page Views| Analytics
    AdminApp -.->|Admin Actions| Logs

    %% Environment Separation
    Edge ---|Main Branch| ProdEdge
    Edge ---|PR Branches| PreviewEdge
    APIApp ---|Main Branch| ProdAPI
    APIApp ---|PR Branches| PreviewAPI
    NeonDB ---|Production| ProdDB
    NeonDB ---|Preview| PreviewDB

    %% Styling
    classDef frontend fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1e40af,color:#fff
    classDef backend fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef database fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef external fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef monitoring fill:#ec4899,stroke:#db2777,color:#fff
    classDef environment fill:#6b7280,stroke:#4b5563,color:#fff

    class WebApp,AdminApp frontend
    class APIApp backend
    class NeonDB,ProdDB,PreviewDB,DevDB database
    class Clerk,MercadoPago,Cloudinary external
    class Analytics,Logs monitoring
    class ProdEdge,PreviewEdge,DevLocal,ProdAPI,PreviewAPI environment
```
